room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Pharaoh" by MindGames Rockford in Rockford
review: My wife and I stayed in the area for our anniversary, and last night we did the Egypt themed game. We had so much fun, the owner was there and made it even more fun. The game was creative and well thought-out.

room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Pharaoh" by MindGames Rockford in Rockford
review: We had an amazing time tonight! It was harder than I expected, but we narrowly escaped the mummy's curse. I cannot recommend this enough for a night out. Total change of pace for entertainment. Try it!

room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Pharaoh" by MindGames Rockford in Rockford
review: We had so much fun! The Secrets of the Pharaoh room exceeded our expectations!

room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Pharaoh" by MindGames Rockford in Rockford
